metadata.name: PUT IN YOUR ANUS
metadata.description:
Putin, the aggressor, and invader has started a war. The world will no longer be the same. He came to our house in Ukraine to kill our people.
Let's fight for freedom together!
All money from the sold works will be managed by me personally and directed to help.
The collector will receive a stickerpack of all the works in this collection when the war is over.
Peace be with you all
